OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779984666
OL,3,CO'Neill signs contract extension to
OL,4,Cremain as NI manager
OL,6,FMichael O'Neill has his sights set on
OL,7,Ftaking Northern Ireland back to a
OL,8,Fmajor tournament after signing a new
OL,9,Ffour-year contract to stay as manager.
OL,11,FIt comes just two weeks after the 56-
OL,12,Fyear-old turned down an offer from
OL,13,FBlackburn.
OL,15,FO'Neill finished the season juggling
OL,16,Fdual roles with Northern Ireland and
OL,17,FBlackburn and entered talks with the
OL,18,FChampionship club over extending his
OL,19,Fstay at Ewood Park after guiding them
OL,20,Fto safety.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779984666
OL,3,CO'Neill signs contract extension to
OL,4,Cremain as NI manager
OL,6,FBut having chosen to stay in
OL,7,Finternational football O'Neill has
OL,8,Fcommitted himself to the Irish
OL,9,FFootball Association on fresh terms
OL,10,Fthat run until 2032.
OL,12,FO'Neill had spoken positively of his
OL,13,Ftime with Blackburn but said he
OL,14,Fultimately felt he could not walk away
OL,15,Ffrom a young, rapidly developing
OL,16,FNorthern Ireland squad who have their
OL,17,Fsights set on qualifying for Euro 2028.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
