CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779984666
OL,3,CO'Neill signs contract extension to
OL,4,Cremain as NI manager
OL,6,F"As much as I enjoyed my time (at
OL,7,FBlackburn) and the people there are
OL,8,Freally, really good people, and Suhail
OL,9,F(Shaikh, chief operating officer) was
OL,10,Fa really good man to work for, I just
OL,11,Fdidn't feel it was the right thing for
OL,12,Fme stepping away from the
OL,13,Finternational job at this minute in
OL,14,Ftime."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
