PN,44704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779984666
OL,3,CO'Neill signs contract extension to
OL,4,Cremain as NI manager
OL,6,FO'Neill took the Blackburn job just
OL,7,Fsix weeks before Northern Ireland's
OL,8,FWorld Cup qualifying play-off away to
OL,9,FItaly, a match they lost 2-0 in
OL,10,FBergamo before playing a similarly
OL,11,Fdisappointed Wales side in a friendly
OL,12,Fthat finished 1-1.
OL,14,F"I had a decision to make and I've had
OL,15,Fthat decision to make in the past as
OL,16,Fwell," O'Neill added. "Sometimes it's
OL,17,Fnot always been as public as that.
OL,18,FThose situations do happen.
OL,26,@vD@AOUxD@FO]xD@WOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779984666
OL,3,CO'Neill signs contract extension to
OL,4,Cremain as NI manager
OL,6,F"I felt it was difficult probably
OL,7,Fafter March. I felt the disappointment
OL,8,Fof the players, missing out on the
OL,9,FWorld Cup, but then saw the response
OL,10,Fand how a young team played in the
OL,11,FWales game.
OL,13,F"Where I was with that group of
OL,14,Fplayers, I just felt the right thing
OL,15,Fwas for me to stay. It wasn't a
OL,16,Fdecision that was a financial decision
OL,17,For anything like that.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779984666
OL,3,CO'Neill signs contract extension to
OL,4,Cremain as NI manager
OL,6,F"Blackburn made me a great offer, and
OL,7,FI was flattered by that as well, but I
OL,8,Fjust felt that I'd started something
OL,9,Fhere at Northern Ireland that still
OL,10,Fhas a long way to go.
OL,12,F"There's nothing better than to take
OL,13,Fyour country to a major tournament. I
OL,14,Fhad the experience of doing that and
OL,15,Fit's something I would certainly love
OL,16,Fto do again before my management
OL,17,Fcareer comes to an end."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
