OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779984666
OL,3,CO'Neill signs contract extension to
OL,4,Cremain as NI manager
OL,6,FDefenders Paddy McNair, Dan Ballard,
OL,7,FTerry Devlin, and Eoin Toal are all
OL,8,Funavailable, as are goalkeepers Bailey
OL,9,FPeacock-Farrell and Conor Hazard,
OL,10,Fmidfield pair George Saville and Brad
OL,11,FLyons, and forward Dion Charles, while
OL,12,FLiverpool's Conor Bradley remains a
OL,13,Flong-term absentee.
OL,15,FLiverpool teenager Kieran Morrison
OL,16,Fkeeps his place from March as he hopes
OL,17,Ffor an international debut, as does
OL,18,FBlackburn defender Tom Atcheson, who
OL,19,Fearned his first cap against Wales
OL,20,Flast time out.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
